{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/wild-terrain-main-gif-description.gif?t=1738071515\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wild Terrain is an single-player adventure game where you play as a wild pig. All of your animal friends have mysteriously disappeared, and it's up to you to find them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll have to use your strength and cleverness to get them out of silly, unusual, or even dangerous situations. On your adventure, you'll discover many secrets, activities and hidden parts of the land.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc17\u00a0<strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the life of a wild pig (aka boar)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make friends with foxes, bears and other animals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a vibrant, small-open world and story at your own pace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Animals can follow you, join your journey, and listen to your commands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Changing weather &amp; temperature for different biomes (snow, forest, desert)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Smash and break objects standing in your way</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scavenge for mushrooms, fruits and other foods</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your appearance with various hats (affects your temperature)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/wild-terrain-gif-smash.gif?t=1738071515\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf32\u00a0<u><strong>Smash and destroy various objects!</strong></u>\u00a0You can use your strength to move and discover hidden foods, items and other important secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/wild-terrain-swim.gif?t=1738071515\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\udd8a<u><strong>Travel with your friends!</strong></u> Any missing friend that you rescue will be able to travel and follow you on your adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No matter where you are on your journey, you can always have fun and explore the world together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/wild-terrain-friends.gif?t=1738071515\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738071515","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738071515","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/ef3493939a39bd1a24b7540bc4635434298ffc1e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738071515","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/ef3493939a39bd1a24b7540bc4635434298ffc1e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738071515","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/wild-terrain-main-gif-description.gif?t=1738071515\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wild Terrain is an single-player adventure game where you play as a wild pig. All of your animal friends have mysteriously disappeared, and it's up to you to find them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll have to use your strength and cleverness to get them out of silly, unusual, or even dangerous situations. On your adventure, you'll